<h1>Nanny Share</h1>

<p>More and more parents are turning to nanny sharing as a way to keep childcare costs down while still receiving the highest quality care. Seattle Nanny Network's Nanny Share is a resource for parents to post, search, and match up with other potential families. 	
</p>

<hr>

<h3>Here is how it works.</h3>

<div class="row">
	<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4 col-lg-4">
		1. Create an Account, Add your Address, Add your Children
	</div>
	
	<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4 col-lg-4">
		2. Search for Families Near You on our interactive map
	</div>
	
	<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4 col-lg-4">
		3. Connect with potential families and secure a great nanny share
	</div>
	
	
</div>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<div class="row">
	<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12">Ready?  
		<% if current_user %>
			<%= link_to "Find a Family", find_a_family_path, :class => "btn btn-primary"  %>
		<% else %>
			<%= link_to "Get Started", new_user_registration_path, :class => "btn btn-primary" %>
		<% end %>
	</div>
</div>


